reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best I have used!!
reviews.reviewText: I’ve used so many different type of screen protectors in my life. Starting from the iPhone 5 all the way up now to the iPhone 15 Pro. I’ve also had screen protectors for my Samsung galaxy S 21 ultra. I’ve never had a screen protector look this good, and also have a protector for the top Speaker. I also have the Apple clear phone case and it fits perfectly. I understand some cases are different, but in my use case, it’s very case friendly The installation was incredibly easy. I did skip one step because I knew it would put dust under the screen. I believe the step was step two I just removed the film and put it on the screen and had no issues. It did have air bubbles but they are incredibly easy to get out and I don’t see anymore. The finish doesn’t look like I have screen protector on. For the price and how many you get I don’t think there’s a better deal that you can get. This is not a bot either. I’m a real person to prove that a real person Max Verstappen won the drivers championship by over, doubled of person that came in second place. Just buy the screen protector.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great, but does not work with all cases.
reviews.reviewText: Other than the tight fit, 5 stars. Super easy to install, great feel, great clarity, and even taking it out of your pocket wipes the fingerprints away. My only (and minimal) issue is that it doesn't work with all cases. I tried the Spigen Enzo Aramid and the Spigen Magnetic Ultra Hybrid (Frosted Clear) and each of those cases lift the protector away from the screen. I tried putting a new protector on, thinking I misaligned, but it still lifted the protector, just from the top now instead of the bottom.It works well with my Mous case and the ESR Tough case. No lifting there. Overall great protection and feel, would be perfect if the protector was just a hair smaller.
